    },
    {
      "id": "TaTkf37_-s5VhySJL4HRk",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 13358.564289296615,
      "y": -1211.8326848175566,
      "width": 266.0259110957271,
      "height": 49.56939919747447,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1971c2",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 2,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bFP",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1263950786,
      "version": 3904,
      "versionNonce": 1031171836,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1775799892869,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "demonstrates",
      "fontSize": 39.65551935797957,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "demonstrates",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "bPOiQknrTY4tBs_Nz2YdG",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 9881.90508207121,
      "y": -2496.1493284752655,
      "width": 2163.078304365461,
      "height": 210.60805953867379,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1971c2",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 2,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bFQ",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1551292062,
      "version": 3087,
      "versionNonce": 1319702212,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1775799892869,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "\"\"The current AI research landscape suffers from reduced transparency, which,\ncombined with economic pressures and high infrastructure costs, has led to\nlower reproducibility and fewer opportunities for wide participation.\"",
      "fontSize": 56.16214921031301,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "\"\"The current AI research landscape suffers from reduced transparency, which, combined with economic pressures and high infrastructure costs, has led to lower reproducibility and fewer opportunities for wide participation.\"",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "gE_X3fyVPtWnKghcHNT9s",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 9880.871425995085,
      "y": -2182.518681654823,
      "width": 2163.078304365461,
      "height": 210.60805953867379,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1971c2",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 2,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bFS",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 499675074,
      "version": 3373,
      "versionNonce": 390541180,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1775799892869,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "\"This makes it harder for funders to identify and support impactful research,\nwhile control over AI remains concentrated in centralized silos, limiting public\noversight.\"",
      "fontSize": 56.16214921031301,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "\"This makes it harder for funders to identify and support impactful research, while control over AI remains concentrated in centralized silos, limiting public oversight.\"",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "gA56EWqhvJ_VZx82vnayf",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 9892.235529349693,
      "y": -1890.018681654823,
      "width": 1937.4225451334332,
      "height": 150.17331919671955,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1971c2",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 2,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bFT",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 227369090,
      "version": 3533,
      "versionNonce": 1201837636,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1775799892869,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "\"We may have missed the train on LLMs, but now is the time to\nprepare for the next step: embodied AI.\"",
      "fontSize": 60.06932767868781,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "\"We may have missed the train on LLMs, but now is the time to prepare for the next step: embodied AI.\"",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "04FydnuJycKe6NVFRc2oq",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 14323.147622629953,
      "y": -2466.5485784573234,
      "width": 1199.5286647398132,
      "height": 198.99693601719153,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1971c2",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 2,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bFU",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1265568066,
      "version": 3978,
      "versionNonce": 1781260284,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1775799892869,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "\"We combine established concepts—such as retroactive\nfunding via impact assets, community collaboration, and\ndecentralized physical infrastructure—to build a well-\norganized and transparent funding system.\"",
      "fontSize": 39.79938720343831,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "\"We combine established concepts—such as retroactive funding via impact assets, community collaboration, and decentralized physical infrastructure—to build a well-organized and transparent funding system.\"",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "IzzHjpDpW3ZxVoLZzURBE",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 14330.165762330025,
      "y": -2191.4485925197187,
      "width": 1280.6744380623231,
      "height": 99.49846800859576,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1971c2",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 2,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bFV",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 224314334,
      "version": 3233,
      "versionNonce": 117386692,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1775799892869,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "\"To recognize and reward reproducibility, we introduce Proof-of-\nReproducibility into the funding system.\"",
      "fontSize": 39.79938720343831,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "\"To recognize and reward reproducibility, we introduce Proof-of-Reproducibility into the funding system.\"",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "FaXvJoVJzNcVaO3TeJ0kd",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 10058.918939994219,
      "y": 226.81098898505138,
      "width": 1086.1834309895821,
      "height": 165.60805953867384,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1971c2",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 2,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bFY",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 233645890,
      "version": 2834,
      "versionNonce": 1311146108,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1775799892869,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "\"Let's look at the user flow! And on the right-\nhandside you can see the demo of our developed\napp.\" ",
      "fontSize": 44.16214921031302,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "\"Let's look at the user flow! And on the right-handside you can see the demo of our developed app.\" ",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "WKtlatgRpJDSYewDYoWEM",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 10048.735529349693,
      "y": 503.27496913882646,
      "width": 1202.8500976562482,
      "height": 552.0268651289127,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1971c2",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 2,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bFZ",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 845721502,
      "version": 3437,
      "versionNonce": 1843189060,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1775799892869,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "\"First of all, Cairn platform enable researchers to\nregister research project ideas. In order to register a\nnew project, researcher must first provide specific\namount of PoRs in advance to show participation on\nthe platform.\n\nFirst, metadata is stored on the IPFS via Filecoin\ndata onboarding providers. Then, impact asset for the\nproject is minted on the Hypercert's contract and\nfinally everything is recorded on our smart contract.\" ",
      "fontSize": 44.16214921031302,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "\"First of all, Cairn platform enable researchers to register research project ideas. In order to register a new project, researcher must first provide specific amount of PoRs in advance to show participation on the platform.\n\nFirst, metadata is stored on the IPFS via Filecoin data onboarding providers. Then, impact asset for the project is minted on the Hypercert's contract and finally everything is recorded on our smart contract.\" ",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "LK0i0ZDiAir0bBquQh7pr",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 13912.402196016359,
      "y": 345.63760603615583,
      "width": 1086.1834309895821,
      "height": 331.2161190773477,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1971c2",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 2,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bFa",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1887011998,
      "version": 3718,
      "versionNonce": 184094972,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1775799892869,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "\"Researchers can use fractions of impact assets\nto trade them for prospective funds or for\nservices that enable research execution. One of\nsuch providers is BitRobot DePIN that provides\ndifferent services for embodied AI, such as data\ncollection or access to robotic equipment.\"  ",
      "fontSize": 44.16214921031302,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "\"Researchers can use fractions of impact assets to trade them for prospective funds or for services that enable research execution. One of such providers is BitRobot DePIN that provides different services for embodied AI, such as data collection or access to robotic equipment.\"  ",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "0nAMNd39VEl7QhqSZxERV",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 9959.068862683023,
      "y": 1695.637606036155,
      "width": 1086.1834309895821,
      "height": 331.2161190773477,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1971c2",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 2,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bFb",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1438009666,
      "version": 4124,
      "versionNonce": 161057988,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1775799892869,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "\"Once the project is executed the researcher\nmust provide research outputs, such as models or\ndatasets and all descriptions of research work.\nThe metadata is again stored on the IPFS.\nResearcher must provide enough information so\nthat research can be reproduced.\"",
      "fontSize": 44.16214921031302,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "\"Once the project is executed the researcher must provide research outputs, such as models or datasets and all descriptions of research work. The metadata is again stored on the IPFS. Researcher must provide enough information so that research can be reproduced.\"",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "ff5W0Oh9GKY4EbK7xosGZ",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 14415.73552934969,
      "y": 1404.9056159592692,
      "width": 1086.1834309895821,
      "height": 441.6214921031302,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1971c2",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 2,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bFc",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1351462558,
      "version": 4597,
      "versionNonce": 539332988,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1775799892869,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "\"Transparency is the key for the next step. Where\ndifferent participants in the system can reproduce\nresearch work and provide PoR. PoR must consist\nenough information on reproduction so that it can\nbe verified. Once the PoR is recorded there is\nspecific time window when it can be disputed by\nthe other participants and must be further\nsupported to become valid.\"",
      "fontSize": 44.16214921031302,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "\"Transparency is the key for the next step. Where different participants in the system can reproduce research work and provide PoR. PoR must consist enough information on reproduction so that it can be verified. Once the PoR is recorded there is specific time window when it can be disputed by the other participants and must be further supported to become valid.\"",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "K-S-jtbf8iYeiOSwwkCwp",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 14410.735529349691,
      "y": 1956.2682528565983,
      "width": 1086.1834309895821,
      "height": 220.8107460515651,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1971c2",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 2,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bFd",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 972015362,
      "version": 5060,
      "versionNonce": 198399044,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1775799892869,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "\"Participants in the system also evaluates impact\nof research through voting. Currently the impact\nis determined by the selected experts, but it will\nbe open to voting in the future.\"",
      "fontSize": 44.16214921031302,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "\"Participants in the system also evaluates impact of research through voting. Currently the impact is determined by the selected experts, but it will be open to voting in the future.\"",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "BJUvSS-h7IRk0qF_o9QXB",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 10254.068862683023,
      "y": 3052.1015861899314,
      "width": 1086.1834309895821,
      "height": 496.82417861602147,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1971c2",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 2,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bFe",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 160792798,
      "version": 5270,
      "versionNonce": 1290666492,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1775799892869,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "In the last step the funders can retroactively\nfund researchers and their early supporters if the\nresearch outputs were reproducible and impactful.\nThe project must acquire minimum amount of PoRs\nto be eligible for the funding and the maximum\nfunding amount is limited by the evaluated impact.\nFunding is transferred in USDFC stablecoins and\nis distributed to the owners of the impact asset\naccording to the fractions owned.",
      "fontSize": 44.16214921031302,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "In the last step the funders can retroactively fund researchers and their early supporters if the research outputs were reproducible and impactful. The project must acquire minimum amount of PoRs to be eligible for the funding and the maximum funding amount is limited by the evaluated impact. Funding is transferred in USDFC stablecoins and is distributed to the owners of the impact asset according to the fractions owned.",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "BOwcIZgBXi9emON_nD9O_",
      "type": "rectangle",
      "x": 17694.20621309845,
      "y": -7181.7527718361325,
      "width": 654.1666666666666,
      "height": 924.8883491689802,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "#d0bfff",
      "fillStyle": "hachure",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "dashed",
      "roughness": 2,
      "opacity": 80,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bFf",
      "roundness": {
        "type": 3
      },
