      "updated": 1775799892870,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "PROBLEM STATEMENT",
      "fontSize": 104.86498942051723,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "PROBLEM STATEMENT",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "UW57GqjLELkgqabgSest5",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 18224.76917169524,
      "y": 4728.1251919366505,
      "width": 663.5657352400393,
      "height": 107.68009923112359,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#2f9e44",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 2,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bN4",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1151998158,
      "version": 3393,
      "versionNonce": 1554528068,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1775799892870,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "\"Scientific research in AI faces systemic challenges, including incentive\nmisalignment that prioritizes quantity over real-world impact and reproducibility\nissues that undermine trust and waste resources. Additionally, centralized\ncontrol limits diversity and access, while inefficient funding hinders the\nsupport of projects with the greatest potential societal benefits.\"",
      "fontSize": 17.22881587697978,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "\"Scientific research in AI faces systemic challenges, including incentive misalignment that prioritizes quantity over real-world impact and reproducibility issues that undermine trust and waste resources. Additionally, centralized control limits diversity and access, while inefficient funding hinders the support of projects with the greatest potential societal benefits.\"",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "1q3e4-iYU1-BR5Xes7MuK",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 16527.73551561912,
      "y": 4883.42250542376,
      "width": 2163.078304365461,
      "height": 210.60805953867379,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1971c2",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 2,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bN5",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 432656142,
      "version": 3621,
      "versionNonce": 1250742012,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1775799892870,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "\"Collectively, these challenges create a research ecosystem where meaningful,\nreusable, and socially beneficial work is hard to surface, fund, and scale,\nultimately limiting the potential of AI research to serve broader public good.\"",
      "fontSize": 56.16214921031301,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "\"Collectively, these challenges create a research ecosystem where meaningful, reusable, and socially beneficial work is hard to surface, fund, and scale, ultimately limiting the potential of AI research to serve broader public good.\"",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
