    },
    {
      "id": "NlPHjy9wWzEy6cPUkkliA",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 16535.201015580416,
      "y": 4594.829188439075,
      "width": 2180.320063127788,
      "height": 112.99999999999991,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1971c2",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "hachure",
      "strokeWidth": 4,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 2,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bNc",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1943979666,
      "version": 222,
      "versionNonce": 1611704004,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1775799892870,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "\"AI research faces challenges like misaligned incentives, poor reproducibility of research artifacts,\nlimited access, and inefficient funding, which slow progress and reduce societal impact.\"",
      "fontSize": 45.19999999999997,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "\"AI research faces challenges like misaligned incentives, poor reproducibility of research artifacts, limited access, and inefficient funding, which slow progress and reduce societal impact.\"",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "m0jHkZMXjmx9-dE4AkSxu",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 19349.133555262975,
      "y": 4277.6960991508795,
      "width": 1289.2833251953125,
      "height": 55.202686512891276,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1971c2",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 2,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bNd",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1646769746,
      "version": 2691,
      "versionNonce": 1673860988,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1775799892870,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "\"So, how does Cairn platform aims to solve these problems?\"",
      "fontSize": 44.16214921031302,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "\"So, how does Cairn platform aims to solve these problems?\"",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "5OeQmKWLnKrdT-D7uHuYc",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 19352.39189673432,
      "y": 4381.029432484214,
      "width": 2230.1166992187505,
      "height": 220.8107460515651,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1971c2",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 2,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bNe",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 989789266,
      "version": 2858,
      "versionNonce": 2018979396,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1775799892870,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "\"The Cairn platform rewards researchers retroactively based on the reproducibility of their work and\nreal-world impact, promoting long-term utility and transparency. A decentralized community verifies\nreproducibility claims, while all research artifacts are securely stored on Filecoin for verifiability and\npublic access.\"",
      "fontSize": 44.16214921031302,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "\"The Cairn platform rewards researchers retroactively based on the reproducibility of their work and real-world impact, promoting long-term utility and transparency. A decentralized community verifies reproducibility claims, while all research artifacts are securely stored on Filecoin for verifiability and public access.\"",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "yEuI_ZuK9jepGiivafPcC",
