      "text": "Login video + HF integration",
      "fontSize": 104.86498942051723,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Login video + HF integration",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "uZ_j4GzCEJHjdVIswqjyQ",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 16554.28523077934,
      "y": 5823.67228962707,
      "width": 2418.64990234375,
      "height": 57.70268651289129,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1971c2",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 2,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bNh",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1263370574,
      "version": 2842,
      "versionNonce": 1700840900,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1775799892870,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Social login is enabled because AI researchers are not crypto native and are not familiar with web3 wallets..",
      "fontSize": 46.16214921031303,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Social login is enabled because AI researchers are not crypto native and are not familiar with web3 wallets..",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "lx18myB-O_u5CaLnYHsRx",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 16558.49782470121,
      "y": 5922.422289627072,
      "width": 2503.166585286457,
      "height": 115.40537302578258,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1971c2",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 2,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bNi",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 803394002,
      "version": 2972,
      "versionNonce": 843737212,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1775799892870,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Furthermore, integration with Hugging Face was implemented, as it is the primary platform where the AI\ncommunity uploads open-source research artifacts.",
      "fontSize": 46.16214921031303,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Furthermore, integration with Hugging Face was implemented, as it is the primary platform where the AI community uploads open-source research artifacts.",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "MjhkmPk3a2q-ypYtfMLjF",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 16540.15617024158,
      "y": 6163.233014495693,
      "width": 757.683349609375,
      "height": 131.08123677564654,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 2,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bNj",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1379876818,
      "version": 2628,
      "versionNonce": 1011576132,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1775799892870,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Create Project",
      "fontSize": 104.86498942051723,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Create Project",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "Qkmc1IYc9-FRqIeDbGkjo",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 16543.497824701208,
      "y": 6359.922289627071,
      "width": 2238.8666178385433,
      "height": 115.40537302578258,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1971c2",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 2,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bNk",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1514556686,
      "version": 2977,
      "versionNonce": 308279548,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1775799892870,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "A researcher can create a project on our platform by connecting it to an HF repo and ArXive\npapers, along with providing additional details.",
      "fontSize": 46.16214921031303,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "A researcher can create a project on our platform by connecting it to an HF repo and ArXive papers, along with providing additional details.",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "XFv3PoyBRWB4uT94hzvo4",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 16542.43115396554,
      "y": 6548.255622960404,
      "width": 2257.3833821614585,
      "height": 173.10805953867387,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1971c2",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 2,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bNl",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 98820942,
      "version": 3762,
      "versionNonce": 1047864516,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1775799892870,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "In MVP version data storage on Filecoin is sponsored by our team, so the UI does not yet enable\nthe option to store research artifacts directly on Filecoin when project is created. Currently we\nstore in our local database project data that is later used for reproduction.",
      "fontSize": 46.16214921031303,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "In MVP version data storage on Filecoin is sponsored by our team, so the UI does not yet enable the option to store research artifacts directly on Filecoin when project is created. Currently we store in our local database project data that is later used for reproduction.",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "tnPQJY4J2cC2dK0QLSX4O",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 19353.931153965535,
      "y": 5812.255622960406,
      "width": 2037.3332519531248,
      "height": 115.40537302578258,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1971c2",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 2,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bNm",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 543370190,
      "version": 3506,
      "versionNonce": 1785690492,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1775799892870,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "In the early stage, PoR generation will be done by our team. Helper scripts are already\nimplemented and will be used in the future by other evaluators in Cairn DAO﻿.",
      "fontSize": 46.16214921031303,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "In the early stage, PoR generation will be done by our team. Helper scripts are already implemented and will be used in the future by other evaluators in Cairn DAO﻿.",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "cQx9X_uE0pseE06tIEo_w",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 19373.739503574918,
      "y": 5615.899681162361,
      "width": 780.1666870117188,
      "height": 131.08123677564654,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 2,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bNn",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 435836626,
      "version": 2877,
      "versionNonce": 1367075908,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1775799892870,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "PoR generation",
      "fontSize": 104.86498942051723,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "PoR generation",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "0kAZW7dAuLctsERmriHLE",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 19356.081219069703,
      "y": 6278.570946370625,
      "width": 2037.3332519531248,
      "height": 115.40537302578258,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1971c2",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 2,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bNo",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 835368206,
      "version": 3581,
      "versionNonce": 96135676,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1775799892870,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Once PoR is generated locally, we store project artifacts and PoR on Filecoin for public\naccess.",
      "fontSize": 46.16214921031303,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Once PoR is generated locally, we store project artifacts and PoR on Filecoin for public access.",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "iMGt8kGHsDLA5GbhfOJJU",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 19359.081219069707,
      "y": 5991.070946370624,
      "width": 2069.3332519531245,
      "height": 173.10805953867387,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1971c2",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 2,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bNp",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1465692302,
      "version": 3890,
      "versionNonce": 2000536516,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1775799892870,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "As you can see, in the current version, PoR represents used resources and logs generated\nduring AI model execution. The PoR structure will be better defined in the later stages, as\nit depends on the specifics of different research artifacts.",
      "fontSize": 46.16214921031303,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "As you can see, in the current version, PoR represents used resources and logs generated during AI model execution. The PoR structure will be better defined in the later stages, as it depends on the specifics of different research artifacts.",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "0eJY_3IdSYubSTidaFuUf",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 19355.997834873735,
      "y": 6466.066347829025,
      "width": 768.1166381835938,
      "height": 131.08123677564654,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 2,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bNq",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1559443982,
      "version": 2787,
      "versionNonce": 2000964220,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1775799892870,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Data download",
      "fontSize": 104.86498942051723,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Data download",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "iobtKIqIsOA7FKJkldtDI",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 19363.43115396554,
      "y": 6646.088956293739,
      "width": 2106.100016276043,
      "height": 115.40537302578258,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1971c2",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 2,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bNr",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 398256270,
      "version": 3274,
      "versionNonce": 1171827524,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1775799892870,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Once data is stored on Filecoin it can be accessed through the platform's UI. Anyone can\naccess the data, even anonymous users.",
      "fontSize": 46.16214921031303,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Once data is stored on Filecoin it can be accessed through the platform's UI. Anyone can access the data, even anonymous users.",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "5Of9TTg3RJNUEFvmb6I_c",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 19330.53117024159,
      "y": 7057.2376130372895,
      "width": 2080.2666829427103,
      "height": 115.40537302578258,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1971c2",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 2,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bNs",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 684593102,
      "version": 3495,
      "versionNonce": 567122684,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1775799892870,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Projects that are reproduced and stored on Filecoin can apply to retroactive funding\nrounds.",
      "fontSize": 46.16214921031303,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Projects that are reproduced and stored on Filecoin can apply to retroactive funding rounds.",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "eQqq09ZpxpyjVVHULkHUv",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 19346.189525954473,
      "y": 6891.066347829026,
      "width": 384.8333435058594,
      "height": 131.08123677564654,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 2,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bNt",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1003225294,
      "version": 2809,
      "versionNonce": 1605018308,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1775799892870,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Funding",
      "fontSize": 104.86498942051723,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Funding",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "1a8UG1n5Pxdyj1FICzm_1",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 19330.531170241582,
      "y": 7243.904279703959,
      "width": 1982.7666829427105,
      "height": 173.10805953867387,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1971c2",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 2,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bNu",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 117699858,
      "version": 3731,
      "versionNonce": 1071176572,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1775799892870,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "In the MVP version the funding process is quite restricted and guided. But in the\nfuture, tools such as Hypercerts will be used to provide diverse range of funding\nmechanisms.",
      "fontSize": 46.16214921031303,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "In the MVP version the funding process is quite restricted and guided. But in the future, tools such as Hypercerts will be used to provide diverse range of funding mechanisms.",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "iESKjjDKSivP8SwLzrXHR",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 16557.51451781645,
      "y": 5727.440299550182,
      "width": 1064.2555406358504,
      "height": 54.99999999999997,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1971c2",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "hachure",
      "strokeWidth": 4,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 2,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bNv",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 2047640078,
      "version": 142,
      "versionNonce": 1800514116,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1775799892870,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Now, let’s take a look at the demo of our MVP",
      "fontSize": 43.99999999999998,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Now, let’s take a look at the demo of our MVP",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "ikBeF7sf2NXqjDgSrhbZV",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 19345.52282877022,
      "y": 4670.469603114178,
      "width": 2190.1166992187495,
      "height": 441.6214921031302,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1971c2",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 2,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bNw",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 251877966,
      "version": 3937,
      "versionNonce": 1806175228,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1775799892870,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "- Why would researchers participate? To receive funding and to publish their work in journals and\nconferences that require third-party reproduction.\n- Why would evaluators participate? They gain compensation and if they are researchers they have\nto reproduce baseline approaches anyway.\n- Why would funders provide funds? To promote quality and development in the research field. Similar\nreasons cane be applied here as why AI infrastructure providers are funding HF. \n- Why do we need Filecoin? To establish verifiable and trusted storage of artifacts necessary for a\nworking decentralized incentive mechanism.",
      "fontSize": 44.16214921031302,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "- Why would researchers participate? To receive funding and to publish their work in journals and conferences that require third-party reproduction.\n- Why would evaluators participate? They gain compensation and if they are researchers they have to reproduce baseline approaches anyway.\n- Why would funders provide funds? To promote quality and development in the research field. Similar reasons cane be applied here as why AI infrastructure providers are funding HF. \n- Why do we need Filecoin? To establish verifiable and trusted storage of artifacts necessary for a working decentralized incentive mechanism.",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
